    <div class="faq-a" id="can-the-ai-content-quality-checklist-be-automated"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Roughly 20 of the 50 checks can be automated today, including plagiarism scanning, schema validation, banned-phrase search, and basic SEO checks. The other 30 still require human judgment, especially fact-checking, originality scoring, and voice alignment. Full automation is not the goal. A 40% automation rate plus a focused human editor beats either extreme.</p></div></div>
